Package dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model Description

This package provides methods to access the tresosDB from within a DataModel and the integration of tresosDB models into tresos Studio projects.

The core classes of the model package are:

  • DataModelAccess: Provides support methods to access the tresosDB from within a DataModel.
  • ProjectAccess: Provides support methods to access the integration of TresosDB models into tresos Studio projects.
  • IEntity: This is the base interface from which all tresosDB model entities are derived.
  • v2.factory.TresosDBFactory: Used to create instances of the tresosDB entities found in dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.
